00:04.774 --> 00:07.309
We worked out the average and we can now announce the figure.

00:07.642 --> 00:12.999
The great news is that he is officially the world's shortest living man.

00:13.105 --> 00:15.425
So as the new member of the Guinness World records family,...

00:16.590 --> 00:17.757
...now it's time to go and tell everyone.

00:19.702 --> 00:24.566
Junrey is officially the world's shortest living man so I present to you,...

00:24.950 --> 00:27.337
...to mom and dad, a big C. Congratulations and...

00:28.043 --> 00:31.837
...thank you for giving us your time to measure him today. Congratulations. Yes, well done!

